oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Floor plan designs for Davidson County Court House
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Four images on one sheet of the floor plan designs for the Davidson County Court House. The plans are of the ground floor, first floor, second floor and third floor.
Original design for courthouse was by Emmons H. Woolwine of Nashville and Frederic C. Hirons of New York.
